{"word":"H3760 - כַּרְמֶל - Karmel - kar-mel' - Carmel","slug":"H3760","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כַּרְמֶל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Karmel"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kar-mel'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Carmel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>כּרמל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>karmel</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>kar-mel'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Carmel = \"garden-land\" <ol><li>a mountain on the Mediterranean coast of northern Israel, just below Haifa</li><li>a town in the mountains on the west side of the Dead Sea and south of Hebron</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H3759\">H3759</a> <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:1042 - karmel\">1042</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3754\">H3754</a>, <a href=\"#/H3755\">H3755</a>, <a href=\"#/H3756\">H3756</a>, <a href=\"#/H3757\">H3757</a>, <a href=\"#/H3758\">H3758</a>, <a href=\"#/H3759\">H3759</a>, <a href=\"#/H3761\">H3761</a>, <a href=\"#/H3762\">H3762</a>, <a href=\"#/H3763\">H3763</a>"}]}